      <title>24 小时降息结束全球央行宽松政策年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年是通货膨胀率下降到足以让大多数发达经济体开始放松货币政策的一年，而随着美联储牵头的 24 小时连续决策，这一年即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏里南称石油特许权使用费支付将改善税收行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/suriname-says-oil-royalties-payout-will-improve-tax-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏里南财政部长斯坦利·拉格霍巴辛 (Stanley Raghoebarsing) 表示，政府将只向在税务系统登记的居民支付石油特许权使用费，以减少未纳税或未受到监管的经济部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/suriname-says-oil-royalties-payout-will-improve-tax-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 20:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
